vernac_cmds: Definition func_at (f: funspec): address -> pred rmap := match f with | mk_funspec fsig cc A P Q _ _ => pureat (SomeP (SpecTT A) (packPQ P Q)) (FUN fsig cc) end.
Definition func_at' (f: funspec) (loc: address) : pred rmap := match f with | mk_funspec fsig cc _ _ _ _ _ => EX pp:_, pureat pp (FUN fsig cc) loc end.
Definition func_ptr (f: funspec) (v: val): mpred := EX b: block, !! (v = Vptr b Ptrofs.zero) && func_at f (b, 0).

Definition NDmk_funspec (f: funsig) (cc: calling_convention) (A: Type) (Pre Post: A -> environ -> mpred): funspec := mk_funspec f cc (rmaps.ConstType A) (fun _ => Pre) (fun _ => Post) (const_super_non_expansive _ _) (const_super_non_expansive _ _).

Definition closed_wrt_vars {B} (S: ident -> Prop) (F: environ -> B) : Prop := forall rho te', (forall i, S i \/ Map.get (te_of rho) i = Map.get te' i) -> F rho = F (mkEnviron (ge_of rho) (ve_of rho) te').

Definition closed_wrt_lvars {B} (S: ident -> Prop) (F: environ -> B) : Prop := forall rho ve', (forall i, S i \/ Map.get (ve_of rho) i = Map.get ve' i) -> F rho = F (mkEnviron (ge_of rho) ve' (te_of rho)).
Definition not_a_param (params: list (ident * type)) (i : ident) : Prop := ~ In i (map (@fst _ _) params).
Definition is_a_local (vars: list (ident * type)) (i: ident) : Prop := In i (map (@fst _ _) vars) .
Fixpoint sepcon_list {A}{JA: Join A}{PA: Perm_alg A}{SA: Sep_alg A}{AG: ageable A} {AgeA: Age_alg A} (p: list (pred A)) : pred A := match p with nil => emp | h::t => h * sepcon_list t end.
Definition typed_true (t: type) (v: val) : Prop := strict_bool_val v t = Some true.
Definition typed_false (t: type)(v: val) : Prop := strict_bool_val v t = Some false.
Definition subst {A} (x: ident) (v: val) (P: environ -> A) : environ -> A := fun s => P (env_set s x v).
Lemma subst_extens: forall a v P Q, (forall rho, P rho |-- Q rho) -> forall rho, subst a v P rho |-- subst a v Q rho.
Lemma approx_sepcon: forall (P Q: mpred) n, approx n (P * Q) = approx n P * approx n Q.
Lemma approx_andp: forall (P Q: mpred) n, approx n (P && Q) = approx n P && approx n Q.
Lemma approx_exp: forall A (P: A -> mpred) n, approx n (exp P) = EX a: A, approx n (P a).
Lemma approx_allp: forall A (P: A -> mpred) n, A -> approx n (allp P) = ALL a: A, approx n (P a).
Lemma approx_jam {B: Type} {S': B -> Prop} (S: forall l, {S' l}+{~ S' l}) (P Q: B -> mpred) n (b : B) : approx n (jam S P Q b) = jam S (approx n oo P) (approx n oo Q) b.

Lemma approx_func_ptr: forall (A: Type) fsig0 cc (P Q: A -> environ -> mpred) (v: val) (n: nat), approx n (func_ptr (NDmk_funspec fsig0 cc A P Q) v) = approx n (func_ptr (NDmk_funspec fsig0 cc A (fun a rho => approx n (P a rho)) (fun a rho => approx n (Q a rho))) v).

change (approx (level w) (approx n (Q a rho))) with ((approx (level w) oo (approx n)) (Q a rho)).
change (approx (level w) (approx n (P a rho))) with ((approx (level w) oo (approx n)) (P a rho)).

Definition funspecs_assert (FunSpecs: PTree.t funspec): assert := fun rho => (ALL id: ident, ALL fs:funspec, !! (FunSpecs!id = Some fs) --> EX b:block, !! (Map.get (ge_of rho) id = Some b) && func_at fs (b,0)) && (ALL b: block, ALL fs:funspec, func_at' fs (b,0) --> EX id:ident, !! (Map.get (ge_of rho) id = Some b) && !! exists fs, FunSpecs!id = Some fs).
Fixpoint make_args (il: list ident) (vl: list val) (rho: environ) := match il, vl with | nil, nil => globals_only rho | i::il', v::vl' => env_set (make_args il' vl' rho) i v | _ , _ => rho end.
Lemma same_FS_funspecs_assert: forall FS1 FS2, (forall id, FS1 ! id = FS2 ! id) -> funspecs_assert FS1 = funspecs_assert FS2.
assert (forall FS FS' rho, (forall id, FS ! id = FS' ! id) -> funspecs_assert FS rho |-- funspecs_assert FS' rho).
intros loc fs w' Hw' H4; destruct (H1 loc fs w' Hw' H4) as [id H3].
apply pred_ext; apply H; intros; auto.
Lemma funspecs_assert_rho: forall G rho rho', ge_of rho = ge_of rho' -> funspecs_assert G rho |-- funspecs_assert G rho'.
